<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 15:14:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于价格走低，澳大利亚下调大宗商品收入预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-revises-down-commodity-revenue-forecasts-prices-trend-lower-2024-09-29/</link><description>澳大利亚周一小幅下调了对资源和能源出口收入的预测，原因是多种大宗商品价格下跌和货币走强继续给政府主要收入来源带来压力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 14:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-revises-down-commodity-revenue-forecasts-prices-trend-lower-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对中国内陆“多波”导弹发射保持戒备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-over-multiple-waves-missile-firing-inland-china-2024-09-29/</link><description>台湾国防部周日表示，在检测到中国内地深处有“多波”导弹发射后，台湾国防部处于戒备状态，几天前北京表示已成功试射洲际弹道导弹。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 13:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-over-multiple-waves-missile-firing-inland-china-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>中方表示将着力解决突出经济问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-says-it-will-focus-solving-outstanding-economic-problems-2024-09-29/</link><description>据官方媒体周日援引中国内阁或政府会议报道，中国表示将集中力量解决突出经济问题，努力完成年度经济和社会发展目标。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 11:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-says-it-will-focus-solving-outstanding-economic-problems-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>1-8月国有企业利润同比下降2.1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-state-owned-firms-profits-down-21-yy-jan-aug-2024-09-29/</link><description>财政部周日在其网站上发表声明称，1-8月中国国有企业利润同比下降2.1%。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 09:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-state-owned-firms-profits-down-21-yy-jan-aug-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示反对任何侵犯黎巴嫩主权的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-says-it-opposes-any-violation-lebanons-sovereignty-2024-09-29/</link><description>在以色列对贝鲁特的空袭导致真主党领导人哈桑·纳斯鲁拉死亡后，中国外交部周日在其网站上表示，中国反对任何侵犯黎巴嫩主权的行为。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 07:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-says-it-opposes-any-violation-lebanons-sovereignty-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国在菲律宾部署导弹破坏和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-us-missile-deployment-philippines-undermines-peace-2024-09-29/</link><description>中国外交部周日表示，中国外交部长王毅表示，美国在菲律宾部署中程导弹“破坏地区和平与稳定”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 04:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-us-missile-deployment-philippines-undermines-peace-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>王宣扬中国作为和平缔造者的角色，呼吁中东停火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/wang-touts-chinas-role-peacemaker-calls-mideast-ceasefire-2024-09-28/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周六在联合国大会上寻求提升中国作为全球和平缔造者的信誉，呼吁中东停止战斗，并宣传北京在俄罗斯乌克兰战争问题上的外交努力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 16:00:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/wang-touts-chinas-role-peacemaker-calls-mideast-ceasefire-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>上海证券交易所延迟交易后进行测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</link><description>据国营《证券时报》周六报道，中国上海证券交易所将于周日对其拍卖平台和其他多个平台进行测试，一天前，交易发生了不明原因的延迟。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 11:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，欧盟将于 10 月 4 日投票最终确定对中国制造的电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</link><description>据彭博社周六援引知情人士消息称，欧盟计划于 10 月 4 日就是否对中国制造的进口电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税进行投票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 07:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美会谈后在南海举行军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，在中国最高外交官与美国外长讨论缓解地区紧张局势的方法数小时后，中国军方表示，中国空军和海军正在南海争议地区进行演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国与亚太国家在南海举行联合海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，五国武装部队在南海部分海域举行联合海上演习，而中国则在有争议的水道上进行了自己的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 01:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，币安创始人赵被美国释放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</link><description>据彭博社援引美国监狱管理局发言人的消息报道，币安创始人赵长鹏已于周五从加州一所惩教所获释。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 22:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>与中国会面后，布林肯表示北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“站不住脚”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在周五与中国外交部长王毅的会谈中强调了美国对中国支持俄罗斯国防工业基础的强烈担忧，称北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“不合常理”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管泽连斯基愤怒，中国和巴西仍继续推进乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五，中国和巴西继续努力召集发展中国家支持一项结束俄罗斯乌克兰战争的计划，尽管乌克兰总统泽连斯基否认该倡议符合莫斯科的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:14:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟改变氢能项目拍卖规则以限制中国的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五公布的新条款显示，欧盟宣布修改氢补贴拍卖规则，以限制欧盟在可再生能源供应链中对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>